Class XEDictionaryNode

java.lang.Object
  com.jgaap.distances.XEDictionaryNode

 class XEDictionaryNode
extends Object

Cross Entropy Dictionary Node Each node contains a single event and a hashtable containing Events as keys and Cross Entropy Dictionary Nodes as values to the keys. The hashtable can be of any size. When this node is placed in a tree structure, a generalized Trie is created
